108
00:08:42,140 --> 00:08:47,460
Once she did that, the man with glasses walked over with another well-dressed young man.

109
00:08:49,220 --> 00:08:53,560
After sharing a few words, those two young men shook hands.

110
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:56,900
I didn't realize it at the time,

111
00:08:57,540 --> 00:09:01,660
but it would appear that that's when Ava's job was over.

112
00:09:16,400 --> 00:09:20,680
I guess I always knew that you would be the one they'd send to kill me, Martin.

113
00:09:23,560 --> 00:09:24,780
- Go right ahead.

114
00:09:25,640 --> 00:09:27,740
The drinks are doing their job nicely.

115
00:09:28,660 --> 00:09:32,340
I have no real regrets about what I've done with my life.

116
00:09:32,900 --> 00:09:33,180
(laughs)

117
00:09:36,220 --> 00:09:37,260
Oh, sorry.

118
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:40,580
