129
00:10:09,760 --> 00:10:12,040
You saw me point out that young man, didn't you?

130
00:10:13,060 --> 00:10:16,420
You know, I think I might've done something terrible.

131
00:10:17,380 --> 00:10:19,800
I just brought together a horrible man

132
00:10:19,800 --> 00:10:20,900
and the devil himself.

133
00:10:21,980 --> 00:10:25,220
It was like bringing together Mephistopheles and Faust.

134
00:10:27,060 --> 00:10:28,960
But who the hell cares anyway?

135
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:34,020
Too bad that now that I've done my job,

136
00:10:34,180 --> 00:10:36,360
all these party invitations are gonna get wasted.

137
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:39,680
But the good news is I still have my invitation

138
00:10:39,680 --> 00:10:41,860
to the most important party, don't I?

139
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:44,920
Hey, after you shoot me, do me a favor.

140
00:10:45,340 --> 00:10:47,240
Maybe you can go to these parties in my place

141
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,940
